div.p:
The President of the Republic of Ecuador: Señor Dr. Don Gonzalo S. Córdova, Envoy
                    Extraordinary and Minister Plenipotentiary of the Republic of Ecuador to the
                    United States of America;

And whereas the said Treaty has been duly ratified on both parts, and the
                    ratifications of the two Governments were exchanged in the City of Washington,
                    on the twenty-second day of January, one thousand nine hundred and sixteen;
